      <p>"The SWORD Project" is based at <link href="http://www.crosswire.org">
      http://www.crosswire.org</link>. Other apps under the same banner are <app>MacSword</app>
      for the Macintosh, <app>BibleDesktop</app>, a Java app, <app>BibleTime</app> (another
      Linux program), and <app>The SWORD Project for Windows</app> (aka <app>BibleCS</app> or
      <app>WinSword</app>).
      </p>

